            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "The detection of Japanese encephalitis virus in Megachiropteran bats in West Kalimantan, Indonesia: A potential enzootic transmission pattern in the absence of pig holdings",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ajib",
